  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, double-blind, placebo controlled trial of a combined intervention of zinc,
      albendazole, and multiple micronutrients in improving environmental enteropathy in Malawian
      children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
